    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>We noticed that <code>Config.Init()</code> fails when the connection pool is exhausted.</p><ul><li>Steps to reproduce:</li><li>Call <code>Init()</code> with <code>maxConn=0</code></li><li>Expected: error returned</li><li>Actual: panic</li></ul><p>Stack trace:</p><pre><code>goroutine 1 [running]:\nmain.Config.Init(...)\n\t/app/config.go:42 +0x1f4\n</code></pre>",
