    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>Memory usage grows linearly after the cache worker runs for 24+ hours.</p><ul><li>Observed: RSS grows from 120MB to 480MB over 24h</li><li>Heap profile shows leaked <code>[]byte</code> buffers in <code>invalidateKeys()</code></li></ul><pre><code>go tool pprof heap.out\n(pprof) top\n340MB cache.invalidateKeys\n  50MB cache.fetchRemote\n</code></pre><p>Workaround: restart worker every 12h via cron.</p>",
