    "body_html": "<p>The <code>protobuf</code> dependency at v3.21 has reached end-of-life.</p><ul><li>Current: <code>google.golang.org/protobuf v3.21.12</code></li><li>Target: <code>v4.25.1</code></li><li>Breaking changes: field naming convention</li></ul><pre><code>go get google.golang.org/protobuf@v4.25.1\n# requires updating generated .pb.go files\n</code></pre><p>See migration guide in upstream docs.</p>",
