    "body_html": "<p>Test <code>TestRateLimiter_ConcurrentAccess</code> fails intermittently.</p><ul><li>Failure rate: ~10% in CI (GitHub Actions)</li><li>Passes reliably on local machine</li><li>Root cause: goroutine scheduling timing</li></ul><pre><code>=== FAIL: TestRateLimiter_ConcurrentAccess (0.52s)\n    limiter_test.go:87: expected 100 allowed, got 99\n</code></pre><p>Possible fix: increase tolerance margin or use deterministic clock.</p>",
