    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>New contributors are confused by the event bus retry behavior.</p><ul><li>Current behavior: exponential backoff with jitter</li><li>Max retries: 5</li><li>Base delay: 100ms</li><li>Max delay: 30s</li></ul><pre><code>// consumer.go line 142\ndelay := min(baseDelay * pow(2, attempt) + jitter(), maxDelay)\n</code></pre><p>We should document this in the README and add inline comments.</p>",
