    "body_html": "<p>Under load testing with 5000 QPS, response times degrade significantly.</p><ul><li>p50: 50ms \u2192 200ms</li><li>p99: 120ms \u2192 800ms</li><li>Error rate: 0.1% \u2192 2.3%</li></ul><pre><code>wrk -t12 -c400 -d60s http://api:8080/v1/widgets\nRunning 1m test\n  Avg: 423ms  Max: 2.1s\n  Req/Sec: 4,231\n</code></pre><p>Likely bottleneck: database connection pool saturation.</p>",
