    "body_html": "<p>Database queries lack tracing spans for observability.</p><ul><li>Currently: only HTTP handler spans exist</li><li>Missing: DB query spans with <code>db.statement</code> attribute</li></ul><pre><code>ctx, span := tracer.Start(ctx, \"db.query\")\ndefer span.End()\nspan.SetAttributes(attribute.String(\"db.statement\", query))\n</code></pre><p>This will help identify slow query patterns in Jaeger.</p>",
