    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>Migration <code>0042_add_indexes.sql</code> fails on PostgreSQL 16.</p><ul><li>Error: <code>syntax error at or near &quot;work&quot;</code></li><li>Cause: <code>work</code> is now a reserved keyword in PG16</li></ul><pre><code>ALTER TABLE tasks ADD COLUMN work jsonb;\n-- ERROR: syntax error at or near \"work\"\n-- LINE 1: ...ADD COLUMN work jsonb;\n</code></pre><p>Fix: quote the column name as <code>&quot;work&quot;</code>.</p>",
