    "updated_at": "2024-06-10T11:09:00Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>Payment gateway calls can cascade failures across services.</p><ul><li>When gateway is down, all API pods become unresponsive</li><li>Thread pool exhaustion after ~30s of gateway downtime</li></ul><pre><code>// Current: no circuit breaker\nresp, err := http.Post(gatewayURL, ...)\n// Proposed: use circuitbreaker.Execute()\ncb.Execute(func() (interface{}, error) {\n    return http.Post(gatewayURL, ...)\n})\n</code></pre><p>Recommend: 5 failures \u2192 open, 30s cooldown, half-open probe.</p>",
