    "body_html": "<p>Records are silently skipped during Kafka partition rebalance.</p><ul><li>Affected: 10-50 records per rebalance event</li><li>Consumer group: <code>batch-processor-prod</code></li><li>Offset commit timing issue</li></ul><pre><code>WARN [Consumer] Rebalance triggered\nINFO [Consumer] Partitions revoked: [0, 1, 3]\nINFO [Consumer] Partitions assigned: [1, 2, 4]\n# Records in partition 0 and 3 were in-flight\n</code></pre><p>Need: cooperative sticky partition assignor.</p>",
