    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>Prometheus histogram needs proper bucket boundaries for p99.</p><ul><li>Current buckets: <code>[0.1, 0.5, 1.0, 5.0]</code></li><li>Needed: <code>[0.01, 0.025, 0.05, 0.1, 0.25, 0.5, 1.0, 2.5]</code></li></ul><pre><code>prometheus.NewHistogram(prometheus.HistogramOpts{\n    Name: \"http_request_duration_seconds\",\n    Buckets: []float64{0.01, 0.025, 0.05, 0.1, 0.25, 0.5, 1.0, 2.5},\n})\n</code></pre><p>Without fine-grained buckets, p99 estimation is inaccurate.</p>",
