    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body_html": "<p>Session tokens remain valid after a user changes their password.</p><ul><li>Expected: all existing sessions invalidated on password change</li><li>Actual: old tokens work until TTL expiry (24h default)</li></ul><pre><code>// auth.go:ChangePassword()\nuser.PasswordHash = newHash\ndb.Save(user)\n// Missing: InvalidateAllSessions(user.ID)\n</code></pre><p>Security risk: compromised sessions persist after credential rotation.</p>",
