    "body_html": "<p>Terraform shows drift in production ALB listener rules.</p><ul><li>Resource: <code>aws_lb_listener_rule.api</code></li><li>Expected priority: 100</li><li>Actual priority: 50 (manually changed)</li></ul><pre><code>~ resource \"aws_lb_listener_rule\" \"api\" {\n    ~ priority = 100 -> 50\n    # changed outside of Terraform\n  }\n</code></pre><p>Need to import current state and prevent manual AWS console changes.</p>",
